Class InterpretVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • visitor.InterpretVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitor

    public class InterpretVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements Visitor

    A class that implements the Visitor class. It provides an algorithm for every object of the tree in order to print the relevant output.

    Author:
    Theodor Stoican
